snippet.title: PlayStation - Kaikan Phrase - Datenshi Kourin (2000)
snippet.description:
DESCRIPTION
Kaikan Phrase: Datenshi Kourin is an Action game, developed by Produce and published by Enix Corporation, which was released in Japan in 2000.
